%% vllm-gaudi Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe/Route Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant API as OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant Engine as AsyncLLMEngine<br/>ZMQ IPC
    participant Worker as HPU Worker<br/>In-process/Ray
    participant Gaudi as Intel Gaudi HPU<br/>Device Memory

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (KServe)
    KServe->>API: Forward HTTP(S)/8000<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    API->>Engine: Submit Request<br/>ZMQ IPC (Unix Socket)
    Engine->>Worker: Schedule Inference<br/>Python/HCCL
    Worker->>Gaudi: Execute Model<br/>HPU Runtime
    Gaudi-->>Worker: Inference Result
    Worker-->>Engine: Completion Tokens
    Engine-->>API: Response (streaming/batch)
    API-->>KServe: JSON Response<br/>(SSE for streaming)
    KServe-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference (ModelMesh)

    participant MM as ModelMesh Router
    participant GRPC as gRPC TGIS Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC plaintext

    MM->>GRPC: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC/8033 plaintext
    GRPC->>Engine: Submit Request<br/>In-process
    Engine->>Worker: Schedule Inference<br/>Python/HCCL
    Worker->>Gaudi: Execute Model<br/>HPU Runtime
    Gaudi-->>Worker: Inference Result
    Worker-->>Engine: Completion Tokens
    Engine-->>GRPC: Response
    GRPC-->>MM: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus Scraper

    Prom->>API: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP(S)/8000<br/>No Auth
    API-->>Prom: Prometheus Metrics<br/>(latency, throughput, queue depth)
